TITLE: Method Stubbing with Return Values
DESCRIPTION: Examples of method stubbing with different return value approaches including callbacks.
SOURCE: https://github.com/catchpoint/webpagetest/blob/master/vendor/phpspec/prophecy/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
$user->getName()->willReturn(null);

// For PHP 5.4
$user->setName('everzet')->will(function () {
    $this->getName()->willReturn('everzet');
});

// For PHP 5.3
$user->setName('everzet')->will(function ($args, $user) {
    $user->getName()->willReturn('everzet');
});

// Or
$user->setName('everzet')->will(function ($args) use ($user) {
    $user->getName()->willReturn('everzet');
});
```

